radfu (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add plain UART mode support (-u/--uart option)
  * Add unit tests for protocol and flash operations
  * Fix response parsing for erase and write commands
  * Fix read command validation and alignment checks
  * Remove --usb-reset option (not useful)
  * Remove unnecessary delays after boot code
  * Code refactoring with protocol constants

 -- Vincent Jardin <vjardin@free.fr>  Thu, 02 Jan 2025 20:00:00 +0100

radfu (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix RAU alignment validation for read operations
  * Fix skip ACK after last read data packet (per spec 6.20)
  * Fix OSIS detection to track authentication state
  * Fix write to send exact data size matching range (per spec 6.19)
  * Fix connection to detect existing bootloader session

 -- Vincent Jardin <vjardin@free.fr>  Wed, 01 Jan 2025 18:00:00 +0100

radfu (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add DLM state transit command
  * Add initialize command (factory reset)
  * Add boundary setting command
  * Add parameter setting command (one-way lockdown)
  * Add key management commands (KEY, KEY_VFY, UKEY, UKEY_VFY)
  * Add boot code detection delay for reliable connection
  * Complete implementation of all 20 RA4M2 bootloader commands

 -- Vincent Jardin <vjardin@free.fr>  Wed, 01 Jan 2025 16:00:00 +0100

radfu (0.0.3-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add macOS support
  * Add Linux ARM64 builds
  * Add install.sh script for easy installation
  * Use git describe for automatic versioning
  * Fix man page formatting

 -- Vincent Jardin <vjardin@free.fr>  Mon, 30 Dec 2024 22:00:00 +0000

radfu (0.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release

